About Us
Tufton Oceanic Finance Group (TOFG) is the parent company registered in Cyprus.
Tufton Oceanic has offices in London, Isle of Man, Dubai and Cyprus. Tufton Oceanic Limited is authorized and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Oceanic Investment Management Limited is licensed by the Isle of Man Financial Services Authority to conduct Investment Business. Marine Services (IOM) Limited is licensed by the Isle of Man Financial Services Authority as a Corporate Service Provider and Tufton Oceanic (Middle East) Limited is regulated by the Dubai Financial Services Authority.


